com.lacunasoftware.restpki

Class SecurityContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.lacunasoftware.restpki.SecurityContext

  • public class SecurityContext
extends java.lang.Object
    Reference to a security context in the REST PKI service, which is used to detetermine if a given certificate can be trusted.

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static SecurityContext pkiBrazil
      Returns a reference to the built-in PkiBrazil security context (ICP-Brasil).
      static SecurityContext pkiItaly
      Returns a reference to the built-in PkiItaly security context.
      static SecurityContext windowsServer
      Returns a reference to the built-in WindowsServer security context, which consists of the roots trusted by default by Windows Server.
